description.displayText: Sandra is a wonderful woman who is dependable and always on time. It was an absolute pleasure having her in my home. Not only did she do housekeeping, she also took care of my children with what I needed her help with. It's not everyday you come across people you can trust...

description.displayText: I am a very private person and I do not trust anyone. When I first met Sandra, I could tell from her personality and demeanor that she was someone I could welcome into my home and introduce to my children. I did not retain her services for long, because I needed some help while my mother was away. But, in that time, I came to know Sandra on a personal level and she has become like an Aunt to me. My children range from ages 1 to 7 and she works very well with them. She's very thorough and spotless. My home looked immaculate when she was here and I will retain her services again if need be..

description.displayText: Ms. Sandra is the most sweetest woman you will ever meet. My son is 3 years old and he absolutely adores her. My house has never looked so clean, her work is impeccable! It makes me very sad that we have to part ways, since I am moving. If I could, I would take her with me. I definitely recommend her service.

description.displayText: I wish I could have taken her with me to Florida, The peace of mind and the comfort of having her in my home with my boys was something I am still looking for. She became a part of my family and we highly recommend her to anyone who is looking for a reliable and loving person who looks after their home & kids like her own.
